ge, email spoofing, SPF, DKIM.',3,3),(18,5,'Level 4 ‚Äì DNS','Domain Name System, TLDs, forward/reverse lookups, recursive/iterative, DNS records.',4,4),(19,5,'Level 5 ‚Äì Advanced Networking','ICMP, DHCP, OSI model, TCP/IP model, packet headers, ARP, DoS attacks.',5,5),(20,6,'Level 1 ‚Äì Offensive Techniques','Command Injection, XSS, CSRF, SQLi, File Inclusion, Path Traversal, Buffer Overflows, Metasploit, Social Engineering, Phishing.',1,1),(21,6,'Level 2 ‚Äì Privilege Escalation','Linux and Windows privilege escalation ‚Äî services, kernel exploits, SUID, sudo, UAC bypass, stored credentials.',2,2);
